<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> yecz <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von der
                            <expan>jüdisch<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu sein etwievil
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> frewnd des rats von des prechen
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan>
<expan>laid<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns regniert, niht anheim, die
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir besenten und denn
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> bey <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> selbs
                                <expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> so wir kürczlichst
                                <expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> und bitten ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>, daz ir das in gut von uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> wellet. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in
                                <expan>vigi<ex>lia</ex></expan>
<expan>om<ex>n</ex>i</expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>o<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
